data.title: Blogger: Nutzerprofil: Spyrake
data.meta_description: Blogger ist ein Veröffentlichungs-Tool von Google, mit dem du ganz einfach deine Gedanken der Welt mitteilen kannst. Mit Blogger kannst du problemlos Texte, Fotos und Videos in deinem persönlichen Blog oder deinem Team-Blog veröffentlichen.
data.text: Einführung I'm from Romania, in the SE Europe. Born in the city of Galati, a Danube city. Live in Bucharest for about 20+ years, and now, in a small country village (near Bucharest) named Belciugatele. In Romania we have a continental temperate climate, zone 5-7. Than I can't have, out in my garden, tropical/exotic plants. But I have hardy or half-hardy plants. Some fruiting trees, roses, some climbing plants (clematis, wisteria, lonicera), some decorative trees and bushes, and of course a lot of different flowers. The tropical (indoor) plants are presented here [url]http://hoyaspi.blogspot.com/[/url] I'm not a good writer but I hope you will enjoy my garden :)) At least for the information ....
